%N A319867 a(n) = 3*2*1 + 6*5*4 + 9*8*7 + 12*11*10 + ... + (up to the n-th term).
%C A319867 For similar multiply/add sequences in descending blocks of k natural numbers, we have: a(n) = Sum_{j=1..k-1} (floor((n-j)/k)-floor((n-j-1)/k)) * (Product_{i=1..j} n-i-j+k+1) + Sum_{j=1..n} (floor(j/k)-floor((j-1)/k)) * (Product_{i=1..k} j-i+1). Here, k=3.
